/*
 * © 2025 Platform Engineering Labs Inc.
 *
 * SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0
 *
 * Back-compat shim for callers using `import "@k8s/k8s.pkl"`.
 *
 * The schema split (commit 4dadc5b) replaced the monolithic k8s.pkl with
 * three concern-specific files:
 *   - target.pkl              - Config + Auth (cluster connection)
 *   - shared.pkl              - version-agnostic primitives + ObjectMeta
 *   - v<X.Y>/subresources.pkl - per-version PodSpec, Container, EnvVar, …
 *
 * `subresources.pkl extends target.pkl extends shared.pkl`, so importing
 * any per-version subresources module exposes all three layers. This shim
 * pins the back-compat default to v1.34 (currently the latest stable K8s
 * minor in this plugin's matrix); callers that need a different version
 * can import a specific `v<X.Y>/subresources.pkl` directly.
 */
open module k8s extends "./v1.34/subresources.pkl"
